Package com.mindalliance.configurations

This package contains the Configuration, LogFunctions, GlobalVaribles class The package deals with methods and variables which are used throughout the automation application.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Configurations The Configurations class is a collection of methods which sends HttpURLConnection request to the Web service and gets response and retrieves test data.
GlobalVariables The GlobalVariables class contains all the member variables used through out the application.
LogFunctions The LogFunctions class contains all the logs related methods which are helpful for analyzing the results of the test case.
